		<title>電力会社の責任回避？</title>
		<link>https://midori1kwh.de/2016/10/30/8632?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=%25e9%259b%25bb%25e5%258a%259b%25e4%25bc%259a%25e7%25a4%25be%25e3%2581%25ae%25e8%25b2%25ac%25e4%25bb%25bb%25e5%259b%259e%25e9%2581%25bf%25ef%25bc%259f</link>
