		<title>ベルリン市議会選挙　－　社会的弱者とエネルギー政策</title>
		<link>https://midori1kwh.de/2016/09/04/8490?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=%25e3%2583%2599%25e3%2583%25ab%25e3%2583%25aa%25e3%2583%25b3%25e5%25b8%2582%25e8%25ad%25b0%25e4%25bc%259a%25e9%2581%25b8%25e6%258c%2599%25e3%2580%2580%25ef%25bc%258d%25e3%2580%2580%25e7%25a4%25be%25e4%25bc%259a%25e7%259a%2584%25e5%25bc%25b1%25e8%2580%2585%25e3%2581%25a8%25e3%2582%25a8%25e3%2583%258d%25e3%2583%25ab%25e3%2582%25ae</link>
