		<title>「配電網を市民の手に」その2　－　電力会社との争い</title>
		<link>https://midori1kwh.de/2016/04/10/7984?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=%25e3%2580%258c%25e9%259b%25bb%25e6%25b0%2597%25e3%2582%2592%25e5%25b8%2582%25e6%25b0%2591%25e3%2581%25ae%25e6%2589%258b%25e3%2581%25ab%25e3%2580%258d%25e3%2581%259d%25e3%2581%25ae2%25e3%2580%2580%25ef%25bc%258d%25e3%2580%2580%25e9%2585%258d%25e9%259b%25bb%25e7%25b6%25b2%25e3%2582%2592%25e3%2582%2581%25e3%2581%2590%25e3%2582%258b</link>
